# CreateInvoice.intent , MVP Customer Portal / Billing
# The canonical billing mission, reused across the SkillsTech ecosystem.

mission CreateInvoice

goal
  Create an invoice for a completed order.

why
  Invoices are financial records. Duplicates and negative totals are audit and
  trust failures.

input
  orderId: OrderId
  idempotencyKey: IdempotencyKey

output
  invoice: Invoice

guarantees
  repeated order returns same invoice
  invoice.total is never negative

guarantee repeated order returns same invoice
  because retrying an order must not create a duplicate invoice
  verify test repeated order is idempotent

never
  create invoice for unapproved order

errors
  OrderNotFound
  OrderNotApproved

examples
  given a new approved order -> expect an invoice is created
  given the same order again -> expect the same invoice
  given an unapproved order -> expect OrderNotApproved

verify
  test repeated order is idempotent
  test total is never negative
  test unapproved order is rejected
